  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13067823/cycling-holidays-in-the-lakes-and-mountains-inghams.jpg" alt="View of Vesuvius from Pompei in Italy" data-udi="umb://media/3d447fcd145244e793fd64ab0fbc0a40" /></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">From the picturesque towns along the Amalfi Coast and the glamour of Capri, to the ancient streets of Pompeii, this escorted tour will showcase the Neapolitan’s most popular sights. <br /></span></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 1 </span><br />Arrive into Naples airport where your transfer will take you to your hotel in <a data-udi="umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8}" title="Sorrento">Sorrento</a> where you can settle in and enjoy dinner in the evening.</p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 2 <br /></span>Meet your guide and the rest of the group for a walking tour of Sorrento. Discover the old quarter with its maze of streets and local shops, Piazza Tasso where locals enjoy their morning coffee, and the stunning viewpoints throughout the town where you can admire views over the Bay of Naples.</p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 3 <br /></span><span>In the morning head to Mount Vesuvius, where you’ll be taken to 1,000 metres high (the views are amazing) before walking to the crater. In the afternoon, an expert guide will take you on a tour of <a data-udi="umb://document/97a628d0faaf45f8ab79c097838dfb22" href="/{localLink:umb://document/97a628d0faaf45f8ab79c097838dfb22}" title="Pompeii, Mount Vesuvius and Herculaneum">Pompeii</a> where you’ll learn about ancient Roman life.</span><br /><span><br /><img src="/media/13067823/cycling-holidays-in-the-lakes-and-mountains-inghams.jpg" alt="View of Amalfi" data-udi="umb://media/3d447fcd145244e793fd64ab0fbc0a40" /><br /></span><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 4 <br /></span>Enjoy a full day visiting Capri. This stunning island is a jewel on the Neapolitan Riviera with stylish boutiques and fantastic views. You’ll see the Villa San Michele in Anacapri before heading to Capri Town’s famous <em>piazzatta</em>.</p>
<p><span><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 5 <br /></span>Today is at leisure to spend as you wish. Relax by the pool at your hotel, or jump on the free shuttle to explore Sorrento a bit more.</span></p>
<p><span><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 6<br /></span></span>After breakfast, head off to explore the stunning towns of the <a data-udi="umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47}" title="Amalfi Coast">Amalfi Coast</a>. After a panoramic stop in Positano, the group heads to Amalfi where you’ll see the beautiful cathedral before finishing in Ravello to visit Villa Rufolo.</p>
<span> <img src="/media/13067823/cycling-holidays-in-the-lakes-and-mountains-inghams.jpg" alt="View" data-udi="umb://media/3d447fcd145244e793fd64ab0fbc0a40" /></span><a data-udi="umb://document/61b9b813ca6d419794fd819362771320" href="/{localLink:umb://document/61b9b813ca6d419794fd819362771320}" title="Where to go cycling on an e-bike"><br /></a>
<p><span><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 7<br /></span></span><span>Another free day gives you a chance to relax before heading home.</span></p>
<p><span><span class="geolocation-title">DAY 8<br /></span></span>Transfer back to Naples airport for your return flight to UK.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Tour Includes<br /><br /></h2>
<p>7 nights half board accommodation in a 4 star hotel in Sorrento</p>
<p>Half-day walking tour of Sorrento</p>
<p>Full day visits to Pompeii and Mount Vesuvius and Capri</p>
<p>Full day visit to Amalfi Coast including Ravello and Amalfi</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Departure Dates for 2019<br /><br /></h2>
<p>04 May   18 May <br />07 Sep   21<span> Sep </span></p>
